HYPRE General Release Checklist

A general release is done when HYPRE is determined to be stable and alpha and 
beta release bug reports have been resolved.  These releases tend to occur 
infrequently, are available on the CASC cluster as well as all LLNL supported
platforms and downloadable from the web.  The following steps must be completed
and initialed/reviewed by the responsible project member before the release is
made available to users.


Release Number: _______________________________________________________

Date available to users: ______________________________________________


_____ 1.  Beta release has been available and used for a reasonable amount of
          time.  The Project Lead will determine how much time is reasonable, 
          based on the extent of changes made and other relevant constraints.

_____ 2.  Code adheres to project guidelines

_____ 3.  Developer corrected all bug reports from alpha release 

   _____  3.1 Developer provides updated test cases for regression tests 

_____ 4.  Developer corrected all bug reports from beta release 

   _____  4.1 Developer provides updated test cases for regression tests 

_____ 5.  Appropriate testing, including memory leak checking, has been 
          completed by developer

   _____  5.1 Developer provides test cases for regression tests 

_____ 6.  Documentation is complete; Developer, User and Reference Manuals

   _____  6.1 Update CHANGELOG file with information regarding contents of 
              this release

   _____  6.2 Additional information resulting from alpha release is included
              in documents 

   _____  6.3 Additional information resulting from beta release is included
              in documents 

_____ 7.  Project Lead and appropriate project members review documents

_____ 8.  Software Lead completes the following:

   _____  8.1.  Creates tar file consistent with project guidelines

   _____  8.2.  Runs regression test suite on CASC platforms

   _____  8.3.  Runs regression test suite on all LLNL open platforms

   _____  8.4.  Only when 8.2 and 8.3 are correct; move files to LLNL closed
                platforms

   _____  8.5.  Runs regression test suite on closed platforms

   _____  8.4.  Install tar file on CASC cluster, open and closed platforms

   _____  8.5.  Send an email to the hypre-announce users list
